These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: may, february, march, april, january, june, july
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: country, indie, r&b, d&b, reggae, rock, techno
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: zinnia, rose, orchid, sunflower, balloon-flower, iris, aconite
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, rock-climbing, gardening, board-games, dancing, writing, card-games
 1. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1
 2. the person who growsballoon-flower is the fan d&b##1
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who growsorchid##1
 4. the fan indie is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 5. the fan country is on the right of the fan techno##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who growsorchid##1
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the fan reggae##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the fan rock##2
 9. the fan reggae is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
11. the person who growszinnia is the person who's birthday is in january##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
13. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the fan r&b##1
14. the fan rock is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
15. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the fan techno##1
16. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
17. the person who growsiris is on the left of the fan r&b##1
18. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the fan reggae##1
19. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Birthday      | february  | june        | january | march      | april     | may      | july     |
| Music-Genre   | indie | d&b         | techno   | country | rock    | reggae | r&b |
| Flower         | orchid | balloon-flower | zinnia | rose | aconite  | iris  | sunflower    |
| Hobby     | dancing  | writing         | woodworking     | rock-climbing    | gardening | board-games     | card-games     |

